---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="PRAL Tech – AI-Driven Solutions for Modern Operations">
  <section style="padding: 4rem 1rem; text-align: center;">
    <h1 style="font-size: 2.8rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">PRAL Tech</h1>
    <p style="font-size: 1.4rem; max-width: 650px; margin: 0 auto;">
      AI‑Driven Solutions for Modern Operations
    </p>
    <p style="margin-top: 1rem; max-width: 700px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;">
      Empowering organizations with automation, intelligent workflows, and digital systems that reduce friction,
      increase accuracy, and accelerate results.
    </p>

    <a href="/contact" style="display: inline-block; margin-top: 2rem; padding: 0.9rem 1.7rem; background: black; color: white; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: 600;">
      Get Started
    </a>
  </section>

  <section style="padding: 3rem 1rem; max-width: 850px; margin: 0 auto;">
    <h2>What We Do</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>AI automation and digital workflows</li>
      <li>Compliance‑aligned process optimization</li>
      <li>Intelligent chatbot and customer‑support systems</li>
      <li>Technical setup for small teams and solo operators</li>
      <li>Streamlined HR, credentialing, and operations support</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section style="padding: 3rem 1rem; max-width: 850px; margin: 0 auto;">
    <h2>Why PRAL Tech</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>20+ years of federal and operational expertise</li>
      <li>Clear, simple, human‑friendly explanations</li>
      <li>Fast implementation with minimal disruption</li>
      <li>Solutions built for accuracy, compliance, and scale</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section style="padding: 3rem 1rem; text-align: center;">
    <h2>Ready to modernize your operations?</h2>
    <p>Let’s build something efficient, intelligent, and future‑proof.</p>

    <a href="/contact" style="display: inline-block; margin-top: 1rem; padding: 0.9rem 1.7rem; background: black; color: white; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: 600;">
      Contact PRAL Tech
    </a>
  </section>
</Layout>
